{"tid":2423161,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來kelly變咗 我都變咗","createTime":"2021-02-25T17:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T01:16:09.000Z","uid":307910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd53640bc95c331807929a2ef6aedc077841549a","tid":2423161,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T17:38:44.000Z","msg":"我已經唔係以前嗰個變仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我都會覺得自己可以係一個好純好乖嘅男仔，但係我已經唔再係人若變，變成淫虐變（態）<br />\n<br />\n就算我再同kelly一齊，我都已經唔係好單純嗰個我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如算啦，可能到時再一齊我會學人始亂終棄，做mk仔，我都係摺埋一二邊等死算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nkelly我唔愛你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc1b8216d7bd2f266c8c26ede35cf46b0be9d05","tid":2423161,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"奸奸話屌你老母"},{"pid":"e9f722c50f2795917cd72270028f77d985e21cf1","tid":2423161,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc1b8216d7bd2f266c8c26ede35cf46b0be9d05","tid":2423161,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"奸奸話屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"奸奸係第二個人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa46e7ae22a0f35186f954006797b365d77d883","tid":2423161,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"樓主好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後唔入樓主啲post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada4a7e1957bf513bf40e502da41d39044dcfc08","ti